page.title: 03The Sea-Shore
page.content: Part of our landscape is the sea-shore.Most of the time it is clean but when dogs have been down you have to be careful.There are a lot of different shells;here is a list of them: Common Topshell Elephants Tusk Netted Dogwhelk Keyhole Limpet Pelicans Foot Mussels Queens Scallop Tellin Trough Shell Slipper Limpet Razor Shell These are the most common.There may be other ones that are not so common. There are pebbles and stones and very pretty rocks.Once they are poliehed they are very nice.
